                <li class="statement-item" data-id="s2">I know the office at my institution that regulates the use of human subjects in research. <span class="category-label"></span></li>
                <li class="statement-item" data-id="s3">I can describe the ethical principles of work with animal subjects. <span class="category-label"></span></li>
                <li class="statement-item" data-id="s4">I can describe the ethical principles of work with human subjects. <span class="category-label"></span></li>
